OL,3,CSister of Jo Cox says UK politics is
OL,4,Cin more 'dangerous' state since MP's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FBritish politics is in a worse
OL,8,Fposition than it was in 2016 when Jo
OL,9,FCox was murdered, the late MP's sister
OL,10,Fhas warned.
OL,12,FLabour MP Kim Leadbeater, who
OL,13,Frepresents her sister's former seat in
OL,14,FParliament, said threats to
OL,15,Fpoliticians' safety and the strain on
OL,16,Ftheir mental health meant British
OL,17,Fdemocracy was in a "dangerous" place.
