OL,3,CSister of Jo Cox says UK politics is
OL,4,Cin more 'dangerous' state since MP's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FIn a further sign of the strain being
OL,8,Ffelt in Westminster, Tory MP Elliot
OL,9,FColburn said MPs across the House had
OL,10,Fattempted to take their own lives.
OL,12,FThe MPs were speaking to the BBC Radio
OL,13,F4's show Broken Politicians, Broken
OL,14,FPolitics.
OL,16,FMs Cox was murdered in 2016 by a right-
OL,17,Fwing extremist in her Yorkshire
OL,18,Fconstituency during the European Union
OL,19,Freferendum campaign.
