OL,7,FMs Leadbeater, who represents the same
OL,8,FBatley and Spen seat, told the BBC
OL,9,Fprogramme: "I think politics was in a
OL,10,Fpretty bad place at that time. There
OL,11,Fwas a lot of division. There was a lot
OL,12,Fof anger.
OL,14,F"Sadly, I would say, if anything, it's
OL,15,Fworse. Elected officials not feeling
OL,16,Fthey can always speak freely, not
OL,17,Ffeeling they can always say what they
OL,18,Freally think.
