OL,3,CSister of Jo Cox says UK politics is
OL,4,Cin more 'dangerous' state since MP's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"And potentially, worst case scenario,
OL,8,Fnot necessarily voting in the way that
OL,9,Fthey think they should vote because
OL,10,Fthey know the impact it's going to
OL,11,Fhave on their safety, but also on
OL,12,Ftheir mental health and well-being.
OL,13,FAnd that's a really dangerous place to
OL,14,Fbe. That's not good for democracy."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Mr Colburn, who has spoken
OL,17,Fin the Commons about a 2021 suicide
OL,18,Fattempt, said that colleagues "from
OL,19,Fall UK parties" had attempted to take
OL,20,Ftheir own lives.
