OL,7,FEarlier this year, Rishi Sunak warned
OL,8,Fthe UK could be descending into "mob
OL,9,Frule" amid fears about MPs being
OL,10,Ftargeted by demonstrators over the
OL,11,FIsrael-Hamas conflict.
OL,13,FThe programme had exclusive access to
OL,14,Fpreliminary findings of a 2024 survey
OL,15,Fof departing MPs, highlighting the
OL,16,Fimpact of the job on their mental
OL,17,Fhealth.
