OL,7,FIt also includes new evidence from the
OL,8,FHouse of Commons which suggested that
OL,9,Fmental health is one of the most
OL,10,Fcommon reasons those in Westminster
OL,11,Fcontact its medical services.
OL,13,FMatt Hawkins, co-director of campaign
OL,14,Fgroup Compassion in Politics, said:
OL,15,F"We need to have a national
OL,16,Fconversation about the harm our
OL,17,Fpolitical system is doing to anyone
OL,18,Fwho seeks to work in it or with it.
