OL,3,CSister of Jo Cox says UK politics is
OL,4,Cin more 'dangerous' state since MP's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"Toxic debates, abuse, long hours,
OL,8,Flack of autonomy ` these are just some
OL,9,Fof the issues that are taking a
OL,10,Fmassive toll on our elected
OL,11,Frepresentatives and their teams.
OL,13,F"But the problem doesn't stop there.
OL,14,FThese are the individuals being chosen
OL,15,Fto represent our interests and they
OL,16,Fare having to do so while perennially
OL,17,Fexhausted, often anxious, and
OL,18,Fsometimes depressed.
